WEBVTT

00:07:01.911 --> 00:07:04.046
So let's look to the future.

00:07:04.070 --> 00:07:09.828
I'm thrilled that we now have
a completely new weapon,

00:07:09.852 --> 00:07:13.316
and I should say an inexpensive weapon,

00:07:13.340 --> 00:07:15.839
in our fight against superbugs.

00:07:16.447 --> 00:07:17.695
For example,

00:07:17.719 --> 00:07:20.555
I see far-UVC lights in surgical theaters.

00:07:21.629 --> 00:07:24.958
I see far-UVC lights
in food preparation areas.

00:07:26.046 --> 00:07:28.906
And in terms of preventing
the spread of viruses,

00:07:28.930 --> 00:07:32.102
I see far-UVC lights in schools,